1.2 (2015-09-25)

- Close tab in return to search action
- Fix 404 redirection link
- Update footer to display image ressource like header
- Update translations
- Add comment for images in viewer
- Update 3rd party libs
- Add debug info loading remote URI 

1.1.1 (2014-11-19)
- Fix various path issues when viewer is not in its own subdomain
- Fix a rotation issue on IE8 on series
- Rotate thumbnail image as well on first load

1.1 (2014-10-31)
- Add hidef button

1.0.7 (2014-10-28)
- Some more unit test
- Add a python script to check configuration

1.0.6 (2014-08-04)
- Fix some IE8 display issues,
- Add server side rotation for IE8
- Update 3rd party libs

1.0.5 (2014-07-30)
- Add contrast and brightness capabilities,
- Store image parameters (contrast, brightness, negate, rotation) between images inside a series

1.0.4 (2014-07-23)
- Add crop feature
- Add print feature as PDF, with customizable header and footer
- Add Gd, Imagick and Gmagick handlers with same capabilities
- Change default error level to avoid huge log file
- Do not initialize series if not really needed (improve performance)

1.0.3 (2014-06-26)
- Add missing medium format per default
- Update to latest Symfony-YAML and Atoum
- FIx unit tests

1.0.2 (2014-05-15)
- Fix logo size in mobile view
- Update to latest Slim, Slim-views, Symfony-YAML and HammerJS

